<messaging:emailTemplate subject="CRM Approved: Direct Sales Price List {!RelatedTo.name} {!RelatedTo.owner.name}" recipientType="User" relatedToType="ASI_CRM_Price_List__c"><messaging:htmlEmailBody ><html>    <body>    <STYLE type="text/css">        TH {font-size: 11px; font-face: arial;background: #CCCCCC; border-width: 1;  text-align: center }         TD  {font-size: 11px; font-face: verdana }         TABLE {border: solid #CCCCCC; border-width: 1}        TR {border: solid #CCCCCC; border-width: 1}     </STYLE>    <font face="arial" size="2">        <p>以下のダイレクトセールス 基準価格 登録が承認されました</p>        <p>Please note the following Direct Sales Price List is approved. </p>    </font>     <font face="arial" size="2">        <p>Owner 所有者: {!RelatedTo.owner.name}</p>        <p>Price List Description 価格表説明: {!RelatedTo.ASI_CRM_JP_Price_List_Description__c}</p>        <p>Remark 備考: {!RelatedTo.ASI_CRM_JP_Remarks__c}</p>    </font>    <font face="arial" size="3">                <table border="1" >            <tr>                <th>Sales Item Group(SIG)</th>               <th>Customer Group</th>               <th>Effective Date 発効日</th>               <th>Direct Sales Price 直接販売価格</th>               <th>Ex Price Ex価格</th>               <th>Remark 備考</th>            </tr>            <apex:repeat var="item" value="{!relatedTo.Item_Base_Prices__r}">                <tr>                    <td>{!item.ASI_MFM_Item_Group__r.Name}</td>                    <td>{!if(ISBLANK(item.ASI_CRM_Customer_Group__c),"General Price",item.ASI_CRM_Customer_Group__r.Name)}                    </td>                    <td>                         <apex:outputText value="{0,date,yyyy/MM/dd}">                           <apex:param value="{!item.ASI_Effective_Date__c}" />                          </apex:outputtext>                    </td>                    <td>                        <apex:outputText value="{0, Number, ###,###,###,##0}">                          <apex:param value="{!item.ASI_Bottle_Price__c}" />                        </apex:outputText>                    </td>                    <td>                        <apex:outputText value="{0, Number, ###,###,###,##0}">                          <apex:param value="{!item.ASI_CRM_JP_Ex_Price__c}" />                        </apex:outputText>                    </td>                    <td>{!item.ASI_CRM_JP_Remark__c}</td>                </tr>            </apex:repeat>                         </table>    </font>    <br/>    <font face="arial" size="2">        <p>内容を確認するには下のリンクをクリックしてください: &nbsp;        <apex:outputLink value="{!LEFT($Api.Partner_Server_URL_140, FIND('.com/',$Api.Partner_Server_URL_140)+3)}/{!RelatedTo.id}">こちら</apex:outputLink>            </p>        <p>To view the record, click this link: &nbsp;        <apex:outputLink value="{!LEFT($Api.Partner_Server_URL_140, FIND('.com/',$Api.Partner_Server_URL_140)+3)}/{!RelatedTo.id}">link</apex:outputLink>            </p>    </font>    </body> </html></messaging:htmlEmailBody></messaging:emailTemplate>